definition: to receive/to accept/to enjoy/to bring into/to pay (tax etc)/nano- (one billionth)/to reinforce sole of shoes or stockings by close sewing

sentences.english: Dolce & Gabbana sent out a sultry ensemble of suits and lace dresses.
sentences.chinese: 而杜嘉班納產品主打性感套裝和蕾絲裙。

sentences.english: The fashionista was wearing a Dolce & Gabbana spider web dress.
sentences.chinese: 這位時尚達人穿了一件杜嘉班納的蜘蛛網圖案連衣裙。
